snippet.title: Inazuma Eleven GO: Light & Shadow - Story Trailer 1 (Nintendo 3DS)
snippet.description:
Inazuma Eleven GO: Light and Inazuma Eleven GO: Shadow are released 13 June 2014, on Nintendo 3DS & 2DS.

Available here: http://ow.ly/xnzxK
Official site: http://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-3DS/Inazuma-Eleven-GO-Light-883636.html

Nintendo 3DS on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Nintendo3DSUK
Nintendo UK on Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/NintendoUK
